amathuba anemibandela: Amathuba omcimbi uma kubhekwa omunye umcimbi
okuguquguqukayo okungahleliwe: Okuguquguqukayo okungaba amanani awo ayimiphumela yezinombolo yento engahleliwe
ukwehluka: Okulindelekile kokuchezuka okuyisikwele kokuhluka okungahleliwe ukusuka kuncazelo yakhona

ukuchezuka okujwayelekile: Isilinganiso senani lokuhluka noma ukuhlakazwa kwesethi yamanani
